# Files that must NOT be served publicly (Cloudflare Workers Static Assets).
# Only the web app itself (index.html, game.js, style.css, data/*.json,
# vocab/*_forms.json) should be reachable.
#
# schedule.csv in particular lists every future secret word — never serve it.
.assetsignore
wrangler.jsonc
.gitignore
.github/
models/
__pycache__/
*.py
*.md
*.txt
*.csv
Semordle*
